        <p>Tenta la fortuna con scommesse sportive, giochi, lotterie e tutti i servizi di pagamento offerti da Sisal e Lottomatica.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Invio Denaro all'Estero (aggiornato titolo/descrizione) -->
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <!-- ...existing cash icon... -->
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon icon-tabler icon-tabler-cash" width="44" height="44" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M17 9v-2a2 2 0 0 0 -2 -2h-8a2 2 0 0 0 -2 2v7a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h2" /><path d="M7 10h12a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-12a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-3a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2z" /><path d="M14 14m-2 0a2 2 0 1 0 4 0a2 2 0 1 0 -4 0" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Invio Denaro all'Estero</h3>
        <p>Servizio rapido e sicuro per spedire denaro all'estero tramite MoneyGram e Western Union.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Punto Ritiro Amazon (nuova card) -->
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <!-- riuso icona semplice (pin) già in uso nel progetto per evitare dipendenze nuove -->
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon" width="44" height="44" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M12 21c-4.5 -4.5 -7 -8 -7 -11a7 7 0 0 1 14 0c0 3 -2.5 6.5 -7 11z" /><path d="M12 11m-2 0a2 2 0 1 0 4 0a2 2 0 1 0 -4 0" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Punto Ritiro Amazon</h3>
        <p>Ritira comodamente i tuoi pacchi Amazon direttamente da noi, senza attese a casa.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .services { background: var(--color-surface); padding: 6rem 0; }
  [data-theme="dark"] .services { background: var(--color-background); }

  .section-subtitle { max-width: 600px; margin: 1rem auto 0; }

  .services-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; margin-top: 3rem; }

  .service-card {
    background: #f0f9f0;
    border: 1px solid #90ee90;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: var(--transition);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  [data-theme="dark"] .service-card { background: var(--color-surface); border-color: var(--color-border); }

  .service-card:hover { transform: translateY(-8px); box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); border-color: #32cd32; background: #e8f5e8; }
  [data-theme="dark"] .service-card:hover { background: #1a1f1a; border-color: var(--color-gray); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.35); }

  .service-icon { color: #228b22; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; background-color: rgba(34, 139, 34, 0.15); width: 70px; height: 70px; border-radius: 50%; display: grid; place-items: center; flex-shrink: 0; }
  [data-theme="dark"] .service-icon { color: #90ee90; background-color: rgba(144, 238, 144, 0.15); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .service-icon svg { width: 36px; height: 36px; }

  .service-card h3 { font-size: 1.35rem; color: var(--color-text); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; letter-spacing: 0.1px; }
  .service-card p { color: var(--color-text); font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; flex-grow: 1; }

  /* Card speciale opzionale */
  .service-card.special { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #32cd32, #228b22); color: #fff; border: 1px solid #90ee90; }
  [data-theme="dark"] .service-card.special { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3b1e, #0f290f); border-color: var(--color-border); }
  .service-card.special .service-icon { background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); color: #fff; }
  .service-card.special h3 { color: #fff; }
  .service-card.special p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); }

  /* Light mode: testo scuro per massima leggibilità */
  .service-card h3,
  .service-card p { color: #111; }

  /* Dark mode: testo chiaro e leggibile */
  [data-theme="dark"] .service-card h3,
  [data-theme="dark"] .service-card p { color: #f0f6fc; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) { .services { padding: 4rem 0; } .service-card { padding: 2rem 1.5rem; } }
</style>
